Nollywood actress, Nkechhi Blessing Sunday, has revealed that she will never advice anyone against finding and falling in love despite her experiences in relationships. Recall that the actress recently had a messy breakup with her former lover, Opeyemi Falegan in which the couple attacked each other on social media. However, the actress via her Instagram page on Friday, stated that she is not afraid or ashamed of falling in love again. -Advertisement- She wrote, “Regardless of what I have been through in relationships, l will never advice anyone against finding and falling in love. “Love is a beautiful thing and I am never ashamed of falling in love again. Don’t worry about me, l am good.”